== About txt2tags ==

Txt2tags is a document generator. It reads a text file with minimal
markup such as ``**bold**`` and ``//italic//`` and converts it to many
formats, such as:

- AsciiDoc
- Creole
- DocBook
- DokuWiki
- HTML
- LaTeX
- Lout
- Man page
- MoinMoin
- SGML
- Wikipedia / MediaWiki
